to hammers eventually, most likely the mini-dings, so I could have access to all three damage types.<br>
<br>
Now I'm afraid this would basically just be a novelty rather than actually be helpful; the hammer investment would only be to 18 or at the most 25.  Having 18 in hammers would give an anytime chain and a parry chain while 25 would even out the damage variance a little more and add another anytime chain (I think).<br>
<br>
I would of course be using the hammers for 2-hand damage.  But again, the 18 and 25 specs would only give a 1/3 and 1/2 spec at 50 which would hurt the variance a bit.  I would most likely shoot for a spec of:<br>
<br>
50 HTH  30 Savagery  24 Parry  18 Hammers<br>
44 HTH  35 Savagery  23 Parry  25 Hammers<br>
<br>
Something along these lines.  Any opinions please?<br>
